to be reasonable.

05:35.029 --> 05:36.062
And you and I both know

05:36.097 --> 05:38.631
that there isn't a frozen
dick's chance in hell

05:38.666 --> 05:42.101
that that <i>rat</i>
is gonna be reasonable.

05:42.136 --> 05:44.970
