but a frozen dick in his hand.

06:12.934 --> 06:15.501
Robert,
what are you doing here?

06:15.536 --> 06:19.305
I came as soon as I found out
where they took you.

06:19.340 --> 06:22.408
- My purse, it had--
- Don't worry about it.

06:22.443 --> 06:26.145
