had my guard up.

06:36.724 --> 06:37.756
This isn't on you.

06:37.792 --> 06:41.026
This is on that piece of shit
who did this to you.

06:41.062 --> 06:42.328
You're right.

06:42.363 --> 06:44.263
We need to get
to the police station.

06:44.298 --> 06:46.176
- I want to make a statement.
- You can do that tomorrow.

06:46.200 --> 06:48.178
- Right now, you need to rest.
- No. If they have any chance

06:48.202 --> 06:50.269
of catching this guy,
the first 24 hours--

06:50.304 --> 06:52.037
