and getting better.

06:58.579 --> 07:00.079
Okay.

07:04.118 --> 07:06.652
Thanks for being here,
Robert.

07:06.687 --> 07:10.789
I'll always
be here for you, Samantha.

07:12.894 --> 07:16.228
Robert.
You need something?

07:16.264 --> 07:19.198
Yeah. You hear about this
Hardman-Pierpont Malls thing?

07:19.233 --> 07:21.400
I did.
Alex told me.

07:21.435 --> 07:23.369
- What did he say?
- He said he wasn't too happy

07:23.404 --> 07:25.738
with Donna making him look
like shit with his own client.

07:25.773 --> 07:27.706
Mm. Can't blame the man
for that.

07:27.742 --> 07:29.508
