07:31.846 --> 07:33.546
Robert, are you okay?

07:33.581 --> 07:35.548
Because ever since
that thing with Louis--

07:35.583 --> 07:37.616
I'm fine, Samantha.
Do me a favor.

07:37.652 --> 07:39.652
Get to know everything
there is to know

07:39.687 --> 07:41.487
about this whole
Hardman situation.

07:41.522 --> 07:44.156
You never know how
it's gonna shake out.

07:50.431 --> 07:54.166
Harvey, Louis,
good of both of you to come.

07:54.202 --> 07:55.913
- Can I offer you a beverage?
- Oh, actually, yeah.

07:55.937 --> 07:57.570
because this thing's
ending right now.

07:57.605 --> 07:59.738
- What is that?
- We're doubling the money

07:59.774 --> 08:01.907
that you lost
when Kessler backed out.

08:01.943 --> 08:03.742
This says that Kessler
found out about

08:03.778 --> 08:06.378
the Restoration deal
because of a clerical error.

08:06.414 --> 08:08.447
That's right.
Information was included

08:08.482 --> 08:10.649
on certain deal memos
that were just--

08:10.685 --> 08:12.651
Bullshit!
You told Alex Williams.

08:12.687 --> 08:14.598
