gonna cut it with his board.

08:14.622 --> 08:15.588
They need a head to roll.

08:15.623 --> 08:16.900
Louis is just too stupid
to understand that.

08:16.924 --> 08:19.525
You arrogant son of a bitch.
You always underestimated me.

08:19.560 --> 08:21.594
And you're
underestimating me,

08:21.629 --> 08:23.207
because if I'd wanted
to settle with you,

08:23.231 --> 08:24.797
I wouldn't have called
Daniel Hardman.

08:24.832 --> 08:26.699
I thought you said
you called him.

08:26.734 --> 08:29.835
Did I? I must have made
a clerical error.

08:29.870 --> 08:30.603
Regardless,

08:30.638 --> 08:33.038
it's Louis' firm now,
not yours.

08:33.073 --> 08:35.774
And, Louis, we go to court,
the world's gonna discover

08:35.809 --> 08:37.208
that your firm
can't be trusted,

08:37.245 --> 08:39.745
and then you will be
the king of nothing.

08:39.780 --> 08:41.947
But if you admit
that Harvey broke privilege,

08:41.982 --> 08:43.716
this can all go away.

08:43.751 --> 08:44.950
I see what this is.

08:44.986 --> 08:47.820
You want to use that admission
to come after Harvey's license.

08:49.390 --> 08:50.589
Look at that.

08:50.625 --> 08:53.459
