in you to figure it out.

08:53.494 --> 08:55.894
Let me tell you something
that you will never figure out.

08:55.930 --> 08:58.530
Leaders never betray
their partners.

08:58.566 --> 09:00.299
Let's save
the betrayal talk

09:00.334 --> 09:02.701
for Harvey's ethics hearing,
shall we?

09:02.737 --> 09:03.747
I imagine I can win
this lawsuit

09:03.771 --> 09:05.704
and have it scheduled
by the end of the month.

09:05.740 --> 09:06.872
You do this,
I promise you,

09:06.907 --> 09:08.018
