09:24.258 --> 09:25.391
What does that mean?

09:25.426 --> 09:26.992
It means he's not
just suing us.

09:27.028 --> 09:28.238
He's trying to get
a guilty verdict

09:28.262 --> 09:30.496
so he can use it
and come after my license.

09:30.531 --> 09:31.397
What?

09:31.432 --> 09:33.499
- No, he can't do that!
- He can, Donna,

09:33.534 --> 09:35.701
because I broke privilege,
and he knows it.

09:35.736 --> 09:37.269
But you didn't
break privilege.

09:37.305 --> 09:38.737
I'm the one
who told Thomas.

09:38.773 --> 09:39.605
