Thomas knows.

09:40.908 --> 09:41.674
So what are we gonna do?

09:41.709 --> 09:44.343
<i>We</i> aren't doing anything.

09:44.378 --> 09:46.211
Louis and I
are handling this.

09:46.247 --> 09:48.213
