it was a clerical error,

09:51.385 --> 09:53.852
and you'd be proving we did
what they're accusing us of.

09:53.888 --> 09:55.621
Harvey, I'm responsible
for this.

09:55.656 --> 09:57.523
I want to help.

09:57.558 --> 09:58.957
I'm sorry, Donna, but--

09:58.993 --> 10:00.693
I get it.

10:00.728 --> 10:01.805
