10:37.565 --> 10:39.398
Let's say you find him.
What happens then?

10:39.433 --> 10:41.600
You hear of
an eye for an eye?

10:41.635 --> 10:43.469
That's what happens.

10:43.504 --> 10:46.405
Look, if someone attacks you,
they attack me.

10:46.440 --> 10:49.441
So we're gonna go to my guy
and find this son of a bitch.

10:49.477 --> 10:51.844
But when we do,
we turn him over to the DA

10:51.879 --> 10:53.278
and let them do
what they do.

10:53.314 --> 10:54.246
No, that won't work!

10:54.281 --> 10:56.582
I'm not asking, Samantha.
I'm telling.

10:56.617 --> 10:58.584
If you want justice,
you're gonna get it.

10:58.619 --> 11:00.886
That's the only way
this happens.

11:01.989 --> 11:04.656
Okay.

11:04.692 --> 11:06.458
We'll do it your way.

11:06.494 --> 11:08.660
Just give me the name
of your investigator.

11:12.466 --> 11:15.267
Harvey.
What an unpleasant surprise.

11:15.302 --> 11:18.003
Well, it's about to get
more unpleasant,

11:18.038 --> 11:19.878
